attachments.title: Valar Morghulis: An illustrated guide to all 456 deaths in “Game of Thrones”
attachments.text: Before the “Game of Thrones” Season 5 premiere, The Washington Post took a look back and noted every on-screen death from the first four seasons. Here are all 456 deaths in illustrated form, including who, how, why and where.
